answers.answer: Usually when you have protine in your urine there is a big possibility you have preeclampsia

Hey, I had protein in my urine with my last pregnancy n had to do the 24 hr urine. Come to find out I had preeclampsia. This pregnancy they found a trace of protein n I had to do the 24 hr urine n blood work but I didn't have preeclampsia this pregnancy.
I was told the same thing they told me the first step was to drink more water, but the Dr. said it wasn't enough to be concerned about yet.

question: Hey.... i had clinic yesterday and the nurses were like they found a trace of protein in my urine.. am currently 7 months pregnant and would like to know what that suppose to mean? Is it something bad? Or normal?
title: protein in urine
